Package de.tudarmstadt.ukp.lmf.model.semantics

Class Summary
ArgumentRelation This class represents an oriented relationship between SemanticArgument instances.
MonolingualExternalRef MonolingualExternalRef is a class representing the relationship between a UBY-LMF class instance and an external system.
PredicateRelation This class represents the oriented relationship between instances of SemanticPredicate class.
PredicativeRepresentation PredicativeRepresentation class is a class representing the link between the Sense instance and the SemanticPredicate instances.
SemanticArgument SemanticArgument is a class representing an argument of a given SemanticPredicate.
SemanticArgumentTest Tests methods of SemanticArgument class
SemanticPredicate SemanticPredicate is a class representing an abstract meaning together with its association with the SemanticArgument class.
SenseExample SenseExample is a class used to illustrate the particular meaning of a Sense instance.
SenseRelation SenseRelation is a class represents an oriented relationship between Sense instances.
SynSemArgMap This class represents a mapping between a SemanticArgument instance and a SyntacticArgument instance.
SynSemCorrespondence SynSemCorrespondence is a class representing a set of SynSemArgMap instances.
Synset Synset is a class representing the set of shared meanings within the same language.
SynsetRelation SynsetRelation is a class representing the oriented relationship between Synset instances.
SynsetTest Tests methods of Synset class
